-- Hypermarcas Signs Agreement With Ache, EMS and Uniao Quimica
-- B y   T e l m a   M a r o t t o
-- 2012-03-23T12:49:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-23/hypermarcas-signs-agreement-with-ache-ems-and-uniao-quimica.html
Hypermarcas SA (HYPE3)  signed an agreement
with Ache Laboratorios Farmaceuticos SA, EMS Participacoes SA e
Uniao Quimica Farmaceutica Nacional SA to form a joint venture
and create Bionovis SA, a biotechnical company that plans to
invest 500 million reais in the next five years, according to a
regulatory filing.   Hypermarcas will hold a 25 percent stake in the joint
venture.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Telma Marotto in Sao Paulo at 
 tmarotto1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Francisco Marcelino at 
 mdeoliveira@bloomberg.net  